#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:2
msgid "供应链安全"
msgstr "Supply Chain Security"

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:6
msgid "供应链安全是指确保软件开发和交付过程中的所有环节都是安全的，以防止恶意攻击者在软件开发和交付过程中植入恶意代码或漏洞，从而保护最终用户的安全和隐私。"
msgstr ""
"Supply chain security means ensuring that every stage of software "
"development and delivery is secure, preventing malicious attackers from "
"implanting malicious code or vulnerabilities during software development and "
"delivery, and thereby protecting end-user security and privacy."

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:8
msgid "供应链安全包括从软件开发、测试、部署、维护到更新等整个生命周期的安全性保障，以确保软件的完整性、可靠性和安全性。在当前数字化时代，供应链安全已经成为一个非常重要的话题，因为恶意攻击者可以通过供应链攻击来入侵企业和个人的计算机系统，窃取敏感信息或者破坏系统。因此，供应链安全已经成为企业和组织必须重视的安全问题之一。"
msgstr ""
"Supply chain security covers security assurance across the entire lifecycle, "
"from software development, testing, deployment, and maintenance to updates, "
"to ensure software integrity, reliability, and security. In the current "
"digital era, supply chain security has become a very important topic because "
"malicious attackers can use supply chain attacks to compromise enterprise and"
" personal computer systems, steal sensitive information, or damage systems. "
"Therefore, supply chain security has become one of the security issues that "
"enterprises and organizations must take seriously."

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:10
msgid "可以绕过传统的安全防御措施，例如防火墙、入侵检测系统等。此外，由于供应链中的环节非常复杂，攻击者可以选择攻击其中的任何一个环节，从而使得防御变得更加困难。"
msgstr ""
"Such attacks can bypass traditional security defenses, such as firewalls and "
"intrusion detection systems. In addition, because supply chains contain many "
"complex stages, attackers can choose to attack any one of them, making "
"defense more difficult."

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:13
msgid "供应链安全问题"
msgstr "Supply Chain Security Issues"

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:16
msgid "供应链失陷"
msgstr "Supply Chain Compromise"

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:17
msgid "供应链失陷是指恶意攻击者通过攻击供应商，通过供应商的链路从而进入用户的计算机系统或网络。"
msgstr ""
"Supply chain compromise means that malicious attackers attack a supplier and "
"then use the supplier's links to enter a user's computer system or network."

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:20
msgid "供应链后门"
msgstr "Supply Chain Backdoors"

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:21
msgid "供应链后门是指供应商提供的系统存在预置的后门、默认口令或者预留的调试接口。"
msgstr ""
"A supply chain backdoor means that a system provided by a supplier contains a"
" preinstalled backdoor, default password, or reserved debugging interface."

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:24
msgid "供应链漏洞"
msgstr "Supply Chain Vulnerabilities"

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:25
msgid "供应链漏洞是指供应链软件中存在的安全漏洞，可被攻击者利用这些漏洞来入侵最终用户的计算机系统。"
msgstr ""
"Supply chain vulnerabilities are security vulnerabilities in supply chain "
"software that attackers can exploit to compromise end-user computer systems."

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:27
msgid "供应链漏洞通常是由于软件开发、测试、部署、维护等环节中的缺陷或错误而导致的。"
msgstr ""
"Supply chain vulnerabilities are usually caused by defects or errors in "
"software development, testing, deployment, maintenance, and other stages."

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:30
msgid "供应链污染"
msgstr "Supply Chain Contamination"

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:31
msgid "供应链污染是指恶意攻击者通过攻击软件供应链中的一个或多个环节，将恶意代码或漏洞植入到软件中，从而使得最终用户的计算机系统或网络受到攻击。"
msgstr ""
"Supply chain contamination means that malicious attackers attack one or more "
"stages in the software supply chain and implant malicious code or "
"vulnerabilities into software, causing end-user computer systems or networks "
"to be attacked."

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:33
msgid "与供应链后门不同的是，供应链污染通常是指攻击者在软件供应链中植入的恶意代码或漏洞，并不一定是一个特殊的后门。"
msgstr ""
"Unlike supply chain backdoors, supply chain contamination usually refers to "
"malicious code or vulnerabilities implanted by attackers in the software "
"supply chain, and is not necessarily a specific backdoor."

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:36
msgid "供应链数据安全"
msgstr "Supply Chain Data Security"

#: ../../source/misc/supplychain.rst:37
msgid "供应链数据安全是指隐私、敏感数据在供应链中泄露的情况。"
msgstr ""
"Supply chain data security refers to cases where private or sensitive data is"
" leaked within the supply chain."

